It’s been a year since we passed #HR1 to make sure special interest money stays out of our elections.

It’s one of hundreds of bills that passed the House but never got a hearing in the Senate.

@senatemajldr Mitch McConnell, it’s time for a vote.

On December 18, 2019, I voted to #DefendOurDemocracy and impeach the President of the United States.

@HouseDemocrats have taken our responsibility to uphold the Constitution seriously and the time has come for the Senate to do the same.
